# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:12
translate spanish ss1_cdbb8564:

    # "Ms. Welch starts class by handing out the tests that we did the previous week."
    "La Sra. Welch empieza la clase repartiendo los exámenes que hicimos la semana anterior."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:13
translate spanish ss1_5d9d5d63:

    # gg "How did you do?"
    gg "¿Qué tal te ha ido?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:14
translate spanish ss1_0dbc34a9:

    # pc "I aced it. Perfect A+"
    pc "Me ha salido genial. Un sobresaliente perfecto."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:16
translate spanish ss1_9872da7c:

    # gg "Wow, nice! I might need to study with you sometime."
    gg "¡Vaya, qué bien! Quizá necesite estudiar contigo alguna vez."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:20
translate spanish ss1_edc93756:

    # "She turns back to the front and then Ms. Welch starts lecturing."
    "Se vuelve hacia delante y entonces la Sra. Welch empieza a dar la clase."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:23
translate spanish ss1_ac33b73f:

    # gg "Can't wait."
    gg "Qué ganas."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:24
translate spanish ss1_34213f63:

    # "After that, Ms. Welch starts lecturing and we both turn to the front and try to stay awake."
    "Después de eso, la Sra. Welch empieza a dar la clase y los dos nos volvemos hacia delante e intentamos no quedarnos dormidos."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:28
translate spanish ss1_38327323:

    # "Ms. Welch goes on and on about the questions that were missed the most on the test."
    "La Sra. Welch no para de hablar de las preguntas que más se fallaron en el examen."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:29
translate spanish ss1_60ee67bc:

    # "Then she starts in on what we will be covering with the next test which will be next week."
    "Luego empieza a hablar de lo que vamos a ver para el próximo examen, que será la semana que viene."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:30
translate spanish ss1_18c2b08f:

    # "I try to pay attention, but it's hard when I really just don't care about the subject matter at all, and my mind is going everywhere else."
    "Intento prestar atención, pero es difícil cuando realmente no me importa nada la asignatura y mi mente está en mil cosas."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:32
translate spanish ss1_b4a5181e:

    # "I think about my dad. I think about work. I think about what Ms. Welch would look like without that dress on."
    "Pienso en mi padre. Pienso en el trabajo. Pienso en cómo estaría la Sra. Welch sin ese vestido puesto."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:34
translate spanish ss1_5a4862a5:

    # sst "Right, [pcname]?"
    sst "¿Vale, [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:38
translate spanish ss1_b0461cd6:

    # sst "Good, I'll see you there."
    sst "Bien, nos vemos allí."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:40
translate spanish ss1_4b943e43:

    # pc "Uh, what did I just agree to?"
    pc "Eh, ¿a qué acabo de comprometerme?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:41
translate spanish ss1_f0083f96:

    # gg "You agreed to go to the courtyard this evening to help her register voters."
    gg "Te comprometiste a ir al patio esta tarde para ayudarla a inscribir votantes."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:42
translate spanish ss1_0e03a1ab:

    # pc "Oh God. I don't want to do that."
    pc "Oh, Dios. No quiero hacer eso."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:43
translate spanish ss1_5684dd44:

    # gg "Then why did you agree to it?"
    gg "Entonces, ¿por qué te comprometiste?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:44
translate spanish ss1_51548651:

    # pc "I don't know. I wasn't listening."
    pc "No lo sé. No estaba escuchando."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:47
translate spanish ss1_c2ff44a1:

    # sst "Uhh?"
    sst "¿Eh?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:48
translate spanish ss1_d43b4dca:

    # sst "I expect you to pay attention in class, [pcname]."
    sst "Espero que prestes atención en clase, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:50
translate spanish ss1_2e379803:

    # sst "I was talking about how important it is to vote."
    sst "Estaba hablando de lo importante que es votar."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:51
translate spanish ss1_ef5f7136:

    # sst "And how myself and a group of students are going to be in the courtyard later this evening registering students to vote."
    sst "Y de cómo un grupo de estudiantes y yo vamos a estar en el patio esta tarde registrando a los estudiantes para que voten."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:53
translate spanish ss1_03dfffcf:

    # sst "And since you can't keep focused in class, I expect you to be there to help."
    sst "Y como no puedes mantener la atención en clase, espero que estés allí para ayudar."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:54
translate spanish ss1_3a72700b:

    # sst "You will be there, won't you, [pcname]."
    sst "Estarás allí, ¿verdad, [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:55
translate spanish ss1_403d0486:

    # pc "I'll be there."
    pc "Estaré allí."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:57
translate spanish ss1_3807a033:

    # sst "Good."
    sst "Bien."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:58
translate spanish ss1_50770a51:

    # sst "I'll see you then."
    sst "Nos vemos entonces."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:60
translate spanish ss1_eb0964ca:

